    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140420/extras/e8647b11c1b7ff6bade84d1680e0dfb1.poster.avif?t=1750342390\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140420/extras/e8647b11c1b7ff6bade84d1680e0dfb1.webm?t=1750342390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>《透子在地下世界》是一款探索类恐怖游戏，以美丽而充满氛围的环境为核心。在这个似乎无尽的迷宫中打破循环，透子被困在其中，同时还要躲避她的疯狂跟踪者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140420/extras/68d055d96a1c0c9743da1b1e8e83b1e1.poster.avif?t=1750342390\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140420/extras/68d055d96a1c0c9743da1b1e8e83b1e1.webm?t=1750342390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>游戏特色包括：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 超自然的迷宫和迷阵</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 沉浸式音效环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 谜题和互动场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 对恐怖追踪的反应性玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 有趣的地点和与世界的互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每个角落都潜伏着恐怖</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助透子逃离地下世界，同时避开始终在阴影中等待的跟踪者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140420/extras/21d7da3381304eadca73f2706adc5b27.apng?t=1750342390\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140420/extras/21d7da3381304eadca73f2706adc5b27.poster.avif?t=1750342390\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=350 /></picture></span></p>",
